data.description: An Amazing opportunity is knocking at your door.   Spacious home that's ready for a homeowner looking for some sweat equity.  Generous Private Primary Owners Bedroom Suite and Bath with Private Vanity, Tub and Shower combination. The Secondary Bedrooms are Spacious with a Nice Size Hall Bath. All bedrooms have Good Storage Closet Areas. The Size of This House is Complimented by a Large Daylight Family Room with Fireplace.  The lot is built for fun and entertainment.
